OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FVery warm
OL,6,Finto the evening, with late sunshine
OL,7,Finland and some low cloud near some
OL,8,Fcoastal districts. Sporadic showery
OL,9,Frain and some thundery outbreaks will
OL,10,Fspread northeast later in the night,
OL,11,Fwith strong, gusty winds, hail and
OL,12,Fdownpours possible locally.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FStill very warm with some hazy
OL,15,Fsunny spells, but with lengthier
OL,16,Fcloudier periods and some thundery
OL,17,Fshowers, greatest early and late.
OL,18,FFeeling humid. Mainly light winds, but
OL,19,Fgusty near showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
