OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStill
OL,6,Fvery warm with some hazy sunshine
OL,7,FSaturday, however successive showery
OL,8,Fand thundery outbreaks pushing
OL,9,Feastwards will introduce fresher
OL,10,Fconditions over the weekend. Nearer
OL,11,Fnormal temperatures Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
